2038
01:32:47,080 --> 01:32:47,580
definert.

2039
01:32:47,580 --> 01:32:48,496
Og vi skal snakke om--

2040
01:32:48,496 --> 01:32:49,400
PUBLIKUM: Internett.

2041
01:32:49,400 --> 01:32:50,441
>> DAVID MALAN: En Internett.

2042
01:32:50,441 --> 01:32:55,330
Så jeg kunne bare backup lokalt til min egen
hjem, backup-server, eller cloud server,

2043
01:32:55,330 --> 01:32:56,007
